RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE DECISION OF THE CLAIMS
COMMISSIONER TO DISMISS THE CLAIM AGAINST THE STATE OF
THE ESTATE OF PATRICK CAMERA, ADMINISTRATOR FRANK
CAMERA.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the decision of the Claims Commissioner, file number 27606 of
2 said commissioner, ordering the dismissal of the claim against the state
3 of the Estate of Patrick Camera, Administrator Frank Camera, is
4 confirmed.
